{"type": "article", "id": 27728, "title": "带兔耳的储物柜", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-03T06:59:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 37, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144922uweSFPJNr15HciVD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>Sanna Lindström 和 Matilda Lindblom 是两位充满想象力的设计师，他们联手为孩子设计的这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.sannalindstrom.se/rabbitbox.html\">Rabbit Box</a> 的储物盒或许会让喜欢小动物的成年人都感叹自己被种草。由皮革制成的粉红色“兔耳”实际上是盖子的把手，看上去就好像魔术师从帽子中拉出长长的兔子耳朵一样，非常可爱。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144920tf2pYkdWIeui3b8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.6498994\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144921ShHw0gqXDcV9vN1P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144921zsx5IL3Dg9Yqe8am.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32686084\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}